did.unittitle: Business Collection
did.abstract: This collection contains items related to business activity in Cornwall.

custodhist.head: Provenance
custodhist.p: The items in this collection were initially collected by local historian E.C. Starr, but organized and expanded upon by former Cornwall Historical Society president Michael Gannett.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Published citations should take the following form:
Identification of item, date (if known); The Business Collection; MS008; box number; folder number; Cornwall Historical Society

bioghist.head: Historical/Biographical Note
bioghist.p: The documents include both items related to businesses located in Cornwall, as well as non-local businesses that Cornwall residents patronized.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Note
scopecontent.p: The documents include both items related to businesses located in Cornwall, as well as non-local businesses that Cornwall residents patronized from 1767 to 1999. The items in this collection were initially collected by local historian E.C. Starr, but organized and expanded upon by former Cornwall Historical Society president Michael Gannett.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: This collection is arranged in two series, businesses located in Cornwall and businesses not located in Cornwall, then alphabetically and chronologically within each series.
The files are grouped into 2 series:
